  note    = {56\% of 48 HSE patients had anti-NMDAR antibodies of any class (IgG 25\%, IgM 29\%, IgA 27\%). Only IgG correlated with impaired cognitive recovery; IgM and IgA did not predict subsequent IgG autoimmunization.}
