  keywords = {epigenetics, post-infectious, immune suppression, wound repair, trained immunity},
  note     = {Mechanistic review. Post-infectious epigenetic scars impair both the pro-inflammatory AND the wound repair arms of immunity. Relevant to ME/CFS as a post-infectious condition with known immune epigenetic dysregulation. Certainty: 0.60 (review; mechanism well-supported; ME/CFS applicability is inferential).}
