                  throughout neuroendocrine tissues (hypothalamus, pituitary,
                  pancreatic islets, hippocampus, neurons broadly). Required
                  for normal accumulation of neurotransmitters norepinephrine,
                  dopamine and serotonin in the brain. Required for normal
                  accumulation of secretory vesicles in hippocampus and pituitary.
