                  melanotroph proliferation/POMC expression. Can dephosphorylate
                  PI(3)P and PI(4,5)P2 (functional significance debated).
                  RELEVANCE: broad neuroendocrine role explains why hypomethylation
                  (potentially altered expression) could impact cognitive and
                  autonomic symptoms in ME/CFS.}
}

